{
  "__inputs": [
    {
      "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
      "label": "Prometheus",
      "type": "datasource",
      "pluginId": "prometheus",
      "pluginName": "Prometheus"
    }
  ],
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": {
          "type": "grafana",
          "uid": "-- Grafana --"
        },
        "enable": true,
        "hide": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "name": "Annotations & Alerts",
        "type": "dashboard"
      }
    ]
  },
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 0,
  "links": [
    {
      "asDropdown": false,
      "icon": "external link",
      "includeVars": false,
      "keepTime": true,
      "targetBlank": true,
      "title": "Open Grafana Explore",
      "type": "link",
      "url": "/explore"
    }
  ],
  "panels": [
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "decimals": 2,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "reqps"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum(rate(botcheck_runs_created_total[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "runs",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Run Volume",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "decimals": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 1
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 5
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 6,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum(increase(botcheck_run_state_transitions_total{to_state=~\"failed|error\"}[6h]))",
          "legendFormat": "failed_terminal_runs",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Failed Runs (6h)",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 18,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 4,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false
          },
          "unit": "s"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull",
            "max"
          ],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, trigger_source) (rate(botcheck_run_e2e_latency_seconds_bucket[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{trigger_source}}",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Run E2E P95 by Trigger Source",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 12,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 4,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false
          },
          "unit": "s"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 5
      },
      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull",
            "max"
          ],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, trigger_source) (rate(botcheck_judge_run_duration_seconds_bucket{outcome=\"success\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "judge.run {{trigger_source}}",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, trigger_source) (rate(botcheck_judge_llm_latency_seconds_bucket[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "judge.llm {{trigger_source}}",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Slowest Judge Segments",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 18,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 4,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 8
      },
      "id": 5,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull",
            "max"
          ],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by (provider, service, component) (increase(botcheck_provider_circuit_rejections_total[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{provider}} / {{service}} / {{component}} rejections",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by (provider, service, model, outcome) (rate(botcheck_provider_api_calls_total{outcome!=\"success\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{provider}} / {{service}} / {{model}} / {{outcome}}",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Provider Hotspots",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 10,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 13
      },
      "id": 6,
      "options": {
        "content": "## Tempo Trace Drilldowns\n\nPaste these into Grafana Explore -> Tempo:\n\n- Recent root traces: `{ name = \"run.lifecycle\" }`\n- Scheduled traces: `{ name = \"run.lifecycle\" && trigger.source = \"scheduled\" }`\n- SIP dispatch traces: `{ name = \"dispatch.sip\" }`\n- Direct-HTTP harness traces: `{ name = \"harness.session\" && transport.kind = \"http\" }`\n- Judge traces: `{ name = \"judge.run\" }`\n\nUse the surrounding Prometheus panels to identify the bad window first, then constrain Explore to that time range and add `run.id`, `tenant.id`, `scenario.kind`, or `schedule.id` filters as needed.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.1.0",
      "title": "Tempo Drilldown Recipes",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 10,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 16
      },
      "id": 7,
      "options": {
        "content": "## Correlation Workflow\n\n1. Use **Run Volume**, **Failed Runs**, or the latency panels to find the bad window.\n2. Open Grafana Explore and search `run.lifecycle` or `judge.run` spans in that same range.\n3. Pivot across services using the shared fields:\n   - `run.id`\n   - `tenant.id`\n   - `scenario.kind`\n   - `trigger.source`\n   - `schedule.id`\n   - `transport.kind`\n4. Until Loki shipping lands, use local service logs for the rich narrative:\n   - `docker compose logs api | rg '<run_id|trace_id>'`\n   - `docker compose logs agent | rg '<run_id|trace_id>'`\n   - `docker compose logs judge | rg '<run_id|trace_id>'`\n\nSampling note: BotCheck currently uses the default parent-based always-on SDK sampler. There is no Alloy tail-sampling policy yet, so traces should be considered complete but unsampled by default.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.1.0",
      "title": "Trace To Log Pivot",
      "type": "text"
    }
  ],
  "refresh": "30s",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "style": "dark",
  "tags": [
    "botcheck",
    "observability",
    "tracing"
  ],
  "templating": {
    "list": []
  },
  "time": {
    "from": "now-6h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {},
  "timezone": "",
  "title": "BotCheck Run Tracing",
  "uid": "botcheck-run-tracing-v1",
  "version": 1,
  "weekStart": ""
}
